                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- DO NOT disable PowerUIAgent daemon in iCleaner.\n"
                },              
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- The battery can charge a bit over the defined target charge percentage, by 1% or 2%.\n"
